<div id="attachment_8015" style="width: 205px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00558Q74K/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B00558Q74K&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=httpwwwkmweil-20&amp;linkId=RPDYUZD2YIXPSQGQ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img class="wp-image-8015 size-medium" src="http://www.helpingwritersbecomeauthors.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Knowing-Me-Knowing-God-by-Malcolm-Goldsmith-195x300.jpg" alt="Knowing Me, Knowing God by Malcolm Goldsmith" width="195" height="300" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text"><strong>3.</strong> <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00558Q74K/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B00558Q74K&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=httpwwwkmweil-20&amp;linkId=RPDYUZD2YIXPSQGQ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><em>Knowing Me, Knowing God</em></a> by Malcolm Goldsmith</p></div>
<div id="attachment_8016" style="width: 208px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00DEUQ9GW/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B00DEUQ9GW&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=httpwwwkmweil-20&amp;linkId=KZF3MOA5XRXNP27A" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img class="wp-image-8016 " src="http://www.helpingwritersbecomeauthors.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Orthodoxy-by-G.K.-Chesteron.jpg" alt="Orthodoxy by G.K. Chesteron" width="198" height="279" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text"><strong>4.</strong> <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00DEUQ9GW/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B00DEUQ9GW&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=httpwwwkmweil-20&amp;linkId=KZF3MOA5XRXNP27A" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><em>Orthodoxy</em></a> by G.K. Chesteron</p></div>
