		<title>Most Common Writing Mistakes, Pt. 36: Too Much Introspection, Not Enough Interaction</title>
		<link>http://www.helpingwritersbecomeauthors.com/2014/12/common-writing-mistakes-36.html</link>
		<comments>http://www.helpingwritersbecomeauthors.com/2014/12/common-writing-mistakes-36.html#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Sun, 07 Dec 2014 11:00:08 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[K.M. Weiland &#124; @KMWeiland]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Most Common Writing Mistakes]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[character thoughts]]></category>
